caption: You think this is awkward? Try living a few floors down.
I love a parade.
I etched the glass. IT’S YOU  !!
It's a perfect likeness, George. Right down to the hot air.

You think this is awkward?
Imagine the view from the 5th floor.
Well after 40 years at Macy’s, I think it’s a lovely retirement gift, Fred.
Oh honey look, it’s your inflated ego
How nice. It looks like your ego will be joining us.
The resemblance seems uncanny, but I would have to go down three floors to be sure.
And when it deflates, it'll sound like you too
Remember those cells I swabbed from your mouth?
Herb, tell me the truth, how much do you really spend at Macy's each month?
NOW do you see? Nose hairs can never pass as a mustache.
Who knew the Macy's Parade had a salute to Actuarial Accountants?
Fred we said no anniversary gifts this year...but the suspense is killing me. Can I turn around yet?
I see you’ve made an even bigger fool of yourself.
Don't take it personally, but he's 10 times the man you are.
Why does it always have to be about you?
I have two concerns: I don't see any guide ropes and it's not Thanksgiving.
Happy Thanksgiving. I had you made into a parade balloon.
When does your twin brother get back from Chernobyl?
I’m pretty sure you were given the placebo.
I hope you don't mind, but I invited your inflated sense of self-importance.
So what are the people on the 3rd floor looking at?
I'd hate to be on the third floor.
You should see your face right now!
What do you mean you have an identical twin brother, but not exactly?
I'm getting hints of oak, cherry, hazelnut, and LSD
When you said you were the new head of Macy's, this wasn't exactly what I had in mind.
Look, honey, it's the annual Macy's Accountant's Day Parade!
